# Africa Property Index – Design Rules

## ALWAYS follow these design constraints:
- Font: JetBrains Mono for body/code, Inter/system sans for headings
- Colors: Black and white only. Primary = black, background = white
- Border-radius: 0 on ALL elements — no rounded corners ever
- Shadow: 4px 4px 0px black (brutalist offset)
- Typography: Uppercase with letter-spacing (tracking-[0.2em]) for labels
- Style: Database-inspired, structured, technical — NOT marketing
- Buttons: Black bg, white text, uppercase, mono, brutalist shadow, hover invert
- Inputs: Black 1px border, no radius, mono font
- No gradients, no blur, no soft shadows
